  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and sauté for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the dehydrated onion and bell pepper and rehydrate in the pan with 1/4 cup of water.",
    "Add the shrimp paste kapi and sauté for another 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add the tomato paste and sauté for 1 minute until caramelized.",
    "Add the coconut water, salt, and black pepper, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley and pimenton.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a wooden board and let cool to room temperature.",
    "Refrigerate for at least 30 minutes before serving.",
    "To serve, slice the jelly sauce and serve on top of crusty bread or on its own."
  ],
